{"questionId":"2c685c82-a211-4c0f-9856-cc6b06a5a86e_4","correctAnswer":"36","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Plug $x = 3$ into each function: $m(3) = 5(3) + 3 = 18$ and $p(3) = 3 - 3 = 0$."},{"title":"Solve","content":"$$2m(3) - p(3) = 2(18) - 0 = 36$$"},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>36</strong> is correct."}]}